<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Diamond Circle — Le Rouge Originel</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root{
      --bone:#F4F1EA;
      --charcoal:#1B1B1B;
      --wine:#6B1F1F;
      --rule: rgba(27,27,27,0.12);
    }
    body{
      margin:0;
      background:var(--bone);
      color:var(--charcoal);
      font-family:'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      line-height:1.6;
    }
    .wrap{
      width:min(860px, 88vw);
      margin:0 auto;
      padding:120px 0 100px 0;
    }
    h1{
      font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-weight:400;
      font-size:42px;
      margin:0 0 18px 0;
    }
    .sub{
      max-width:680px;
      font-size:16px;
      margin:0 0 34px 0;
    }
    .tier{
      border-top:1px solid var(--rule);
      padding:40px 0;
    }
    h2{
      font-family:'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-weight:400;
      font-size:26px;
      margin:0 0 10px 0;
    }
    .price{
      font-size:18px;
      color:var(--wine);
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }
    ul{ padding-left:18px; margin:16px 0; }
    li{ margin-bottom:8px; }
    .button{
      display:inline-block;
      margin-top:18px;
      padding:12px 26px;
      border:1px solid var(--wine);
      color:var(--wine);
      text-decoration:none;
      font-size:14px;
      letter-spacing:0.5px;
      transition:all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .button:hover{ background:var(--wine); color:var(--bone); }
    .note{
      margin-top:54px;
      font-size:13px;
      color:rgba(27,27,27,0.62);
      max-width:720px;
      border-top:1px solid var(--rule);
      padding-top:18px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="wrap">
    <h1>Diamond Circle</h1>

    <p class="sub">
      This page is reserved for a small group of principal patrons supporting the production of <em>Le Rouge Originel</em>.
      Participation here is quiet and limited—designed for those who wish to underwrite the film at a meaningful level and receive a deeper window into the process.
    </p>

    <div class="tier">
      <h2>Diamond Patron</h2>
      <div class="price">$5,000</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Prominent on-screen recognition (Diamond Circle)</li>
        <li>Private quarterly production letters + priority updates</li>
        <li>Invitation to private rough-cut screening + discussion</li>
        <li>Premiere priority access (ticket only)</li>
        <li>Signed, numbered archival still (limited edition)</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="button" href="YOUR_STRIPE_LINK_5000">Join at $5,000</a>
    </div>

    <div class="tier">
      <h2>Diamond Principal</h2>
      <div class="price">$10,000</div>
      <ul>
        <li>All $5,000 benefits</li>
        <li>Invitation to an intimate pre-production salon (small group)</li>
        <li>Private post-premiere conversation with Delfine</li>
        <li>Early access to select materials (private / watermarked)</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="button" href="YOUR_STRIPE_LINK_10000">Join at $10,000</a>
    </div>

    <div class="tier">
      <h2>Diamond Underwriter</h2>
      <div class="price">$15,000</div>
      <ul>
        <li>All $10,000 benefits</li>
        <li>Underwriter recognition (highest tier within Diamond Circle)</li>
        <li>Invitation for two to premiere priority access (ticket only)</li>
        <li>A private creative/producing conversation (timed by mutual availability)</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="button" href="YOUR_STRIPE_LINK_15000">Join at $15,000</a>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      Participation includes no financial return or ownership interest. This is patronage in support of independent cinema.
      For questions or alternative arrangements, email <a href="mailto:delfine@delfinepaolini.com" style="color:var(--wine);">delfine@delfinepaolini.com</a>.
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
